title: [Coastal Cliffs, Wrecked Village]
description: Here at the southwestern end of the abandoned fishing village, you find a secluded, spot beneath the lush boughs of a great oak tree.  A corroded brass shrine is still intact, though the wall in which it was mounted has eroded to a pile of rubble.
